{"prompt": "Create a platform for a community music school. The design should be harmonious, featuring a cheerful yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Harmony Music School</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #fff3cd; /* Cheerful yellow */\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #f7e17f; /* Slightly darker yellow for contrast */\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 1.5rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            color: #d4a017; /* Deeper yellow for text */\n        }\n        nav {\n            background-color: #fcf5e0; /* Lighter yellow */\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #f7e17f;\n        }\n        nav a {\n            text-decoration: none;\n            color: #d4a017; /* Deeper yellow */\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #ffdb58; /* Brighter yellow on hover */\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        h2 {\n            color: #d4a017;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .intro-section {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .intro-section img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .courses-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        .course-card {\n            background-color: #fff9e6; /* Very light yellow */\n            border: 1px solid #f7e17f;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .course-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .course-card h3 {\n            color: #d4a017;\n            margin-top: 0;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #ffdb58; /* Brighter yellow */\n            color: #333;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1rem;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #f7e17f; /* Slightly darker yellow */\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #f7e17f;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Harmony Music School</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#courses\">Our Courses</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\" class=\"intro-section\">\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/600x300/FFD700/ffffff?text=Music+Learning\" alt=\"Happy students playing music\">\n            <h2>Ignite Your Musical Passion</h2>\n            <p>At Harmony Music School, we believe in the joy and transformative power of music. We offer a vibrant and supportive environment for learners of all ages and skill levels to explore their musical talents.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"courses\">\n            <h2>Discover Our Courses</h2>\n            <div class=\"courses-grid\">\n                <div class=\"course-card\">\n                    <h3>Beginner Piano</h3>\n                    <p>Learn the fundamentals of piano playing, from basic chords to simple melodies.</p>\n                    <button class=\"cta-button\">Learn More</button>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"course-card\">\n                    <h3>Acoustic Guitar Basics</h3>\n                    <p>Start strumming your favorite songs with our introductory guitar classes.</p>\n                    <button class=\"cta-button\">Learn More</button>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"course-card\">\n                    <h3>Vocal Training</h3>\n                    <p>Develop your voice with techniques for breath control, pitch, and projection.</p>\n                    <button class=\"cta-button\">Learn More</button>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"course-card\">\n                    <h3>Music Theory Fundamentals</h3>\n                    <p>Understand the building blocks of music, including notes, rhythms, and harmony.</p>\n                    <button class=\"cta-button\">Learn More</button>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 40px;\">\n            <h2>Get in Touch</h2>\n            <p>Ready to start your musical journey? Contact us today!</p>\n            <p>Email: info@harmonymusicschool.com</p>\n            <p>Phone: (123) 456-7890</p>\n            <button class=\"cta-button\" onclick=\"alert('We will get back to you soon!')\">Send Inquiry</button>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Harmony Music School. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>"}